style="width: 100px; height: 28px; border: none;">\n      </iframe>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div class="why text-justify">\n    <h3>\n     Why?\n    </h3>\n    <p>\n     It was crazy for me to see that there are so many\n     <i>\n      jQuery\n     </i>\n     plugins for date and time picker and so few\n     <a href="https://angularjs.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">\n      AngularJS\n     </a>\n     directives doing the same\n\t\t\t\t\tin the same way, none of them using\n     <a href="http://momentjs.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">\n      Moment.js\n     </a>\n     (let\'s say, Moment.js is unique!).\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     The question is\n     <q>\n      Why?\n     </q>\n     , I thought\n     <q>\n      it\'s not so hard!\n     </q>\n     .\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     That\'s why I decided to create\n     <a href="https://github.com/indrimuska/angular-moment-picker" target="_blank">\n      Angular Moment Picker\n     </a>\n     ,\n\t\t\t\t\tan easy to use datetime picker that\n     <b>\n      does not requires jQuery\n     </b>\n     and uses the powerful Moment.js to perform Internationalization (i18n) and all the operations on dates.\n    </p>\n   </div>\n   <div class="examples ng-scope" ng-controller="AngularMomentPickerDemoCtrl as ctrl">\n    <div class="example">\n     <h3>\n      Easy to use.\n      <span class="text-muted">\n       Easy <div class="container">\n   <div class="header">\n    <h1 itemprop="name">\n     Angular Moment Picker\n    </h1>\n    <div class="lead">\n     Angular Moment Picker is an AngularJS directive for date and time picker using Moment.js\n    </div>\n    <ul class="list-inline">\n     <li>\n      <iframe allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" style="width: 100px; height: 28px; border: none;">\n      </iframe>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div class="why text-justify">\n    <h3>\n     Why?\n    </h3>\n    <p>\n     It was crazy for me to see that there are so many\n     <i>\n      jQuery\n     </i>\n     plugins for date and time picker and so few\n     <a href="https://angularjs.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">\n      AngularJS\n     </a>\n     directives doing the same\n\t\t\t\t\tin the same way, none of them using\n     <a href="http://momentjs.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">\n      Moment.js\n     </a>\n     (let\'s say, Moment.js is unique!).\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     The question is\n     <q>\n      Why?\n     </q>\n     , I thought\n     <q>\n      it\'s not so hard!\n     </q>\n     .\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     That\'s why I decided to create\n     <a href="https://github.com/indrimuska/angular-moment-picker" target="_blank">\n      Angular Moment Picker\n     </a>\n     ,\n\t\t\t\t\tan easy to use datetime picker that\n     <b>\n      does not requires jQuery\n     </b>\n     and uses the powerful Moment.js to perform Internationalization (i18n) and all the operations on dates.\n    </p>\n   </div>\n   <div class="examples ng-scope" ng-controller="AngularMomentPickerDemoCtrl as ctrl">\n    <div class="example">\n     <h3>\n      Easy to use.\n      <span class="text-muted">\n       Easy
